<h3>Syntax Patterns</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Syntax</th><th>Meaning</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>allow="camera"</code></td><td>Allow camera for the iframe's origin</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>allow="camera *"</code></td><td>Allow camera for any origin (broad)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>allow="camera https://a.com"</code></td><td>Allow camera only for <code>https://a.com</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>allow="camera 'self'"</code></td><td>Allow camera only for the embedding page's origin</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>allow="camera 'none'"</code></td><td>Explicitly deny camera access</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

